high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right.
Pick up the bar of soap that's in front of you in the garbage can.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Get the soap wet in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Back up a step so you can use the cupboard under the sink.
Open the cupboard under the sink and put the bar of soap under and to the right of the soap there already and then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the trash can in the corner.
Pick up the soap in the trash can.
Bring the soap to the sink on the right.
Wash the soap in the sink with water.
Bring the washed soap to the cabinet right of the trash can.
Put the soap in the bottom cabinet next to the trash can, in front of the other soap.
anns.task_desc: Put washed soap in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around then walk towards the door, turn right then walk towards the trash can.
Pick up the bar of soap then turn right and head towards the sink.
Place the soap into the sink, turn the water on, rinse it, then turn it off.
Turn around then head towards the toilet, turn around then head towards the tall cabinet located between the trash can and the sink.
Open the bottom cabinet door on the left.
Place the bar of soap inside the cabinet beneath the other one then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a bar of soap inside the tall cabinet.
